Have a room's settings save.  With some of the commands, most notably 
the description changing commands, the room must be saved or they will 
not be in effect after reboot.  Always use this after making any 
permanent changes that you wish to continue after a reboot. 

Syntax:
[1;37msave_settings[2;37;0m

[1;30mSee also: save_all, settings[2;37;0m
